creator: Graduway
descriptionHtml:
Re-connect with old classmates
Oxford University allows you to both re-connect with old classmates as well as enabling you to utilise the trusted Oxford Alumni Community environment to expand your professional network.

Your Oxford Alumni Community Community
By fully integrating with social networks, and cultivating a culture of helping and giving back, you will be amazed how vibrant your Oxford Alumni Community community is!
descriptionShort: Re-connect with old alumni, give back, and expand your professional network.
title: Oxford Alumni Community
